    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><br>偏玄幻修仙设定，磨练心智才可以晋升<br>与天才少女一起，经历一段奇妙的冒险<br>单结局线性故事，享受跌宕起伏的故事<br>硬核的养成玩法，错一步将会满盘皆输<br>需要思考的战斗，摸索敌人的行动路线<br>多种装备的组合，用不同流派出奇制胜<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/9ce9c29dd4bb42d41d9e68362516db87.avif?t=1766385335\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>《侠道游歌》是一款架空古风养成类JRPG游戏。女神异闻录+炼金工房融(feng)合(he)系统(guai)。<br>神州北寻之地，习武天才吕灵姬受师父陈靖君嘱托前往北寻都城繁城历练，并寻找失踪的养父下落。途中经过万千考验，面对形势复杂的乱世，坚定地寻求属于自身的前进道路，抒写了一曲波澜壮阔的侠之凯歌。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/d5d8ed1290c46e1e04373156dcd79f34.poster.avif?t=1766385335\" width=560 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/d5d8ed1290c46e1e04373156dcd79f34.webm?t=1766385335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/d5d8ed1290c46e1e04373156dcd79f34.mp4?t=1766385335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/c55da187227d320a0b335eb5d3b14b4a.avif?t=1766385335\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>烽火四起，天下战局变幻莫测。依靠山脉天险暂时保得一方平安的北寻内忧外患不断：主战、主和与中庸的三派臣属互相倾轧掣肘。作为北寻都城的繁城更是表面平和，暗流涌动。初到繁城的吕灵姬将这里选为自己成为“侠”的起点，却陷入漩涡的中心。你将帮助吕灵姬离开泥沼之地，贯彻侠道，获得足以平息斗争的强大能力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/daf83420713e05562e5a329550aa142d.poster.avif?t=1766385335\" width=560 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/daf83420713e05562e5a329550aa142d.webm?t=1766385335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/daf83420713e05562e5a329550aa142d.mp4?t=1766385335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/4722749f04530326df27fd9dd3dcced5.avif?t=1766385335\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>玩家将扮演吕灵姬在繁城内外结识多个人物，多达十二位可结缘的特殊剧情角色等待挖掘，在足够了解彼此之后他们或将成为你战斗时不可或缺的优秀助力，或会提供效果各异的强力增益，请根据自己的喜好尽情互动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/35e18cc2bd174af3a2ab9d8d166c4569.poster.avif?t=1766385335\" width=560 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/35e18cc2bd174af3a2ab9d8d166c4569.webm?t=1766385335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/35e18cc2bd174af3a2ab9d8d166c4569.mp4?t=1766385335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186460/extras/4fb3b50c8075451e65ae4a7548630a77.avif?t=1766385335\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>在游戏的自由活动时间内，玩家的不同选择会导致千差万别的结果，不同的结果会影响战斗乃至剧情发展，犹如蝴蝶效应一般。打败敌人取得胜利的吕灵姬将与伙伴们继续新的旅程，一步步揭开埋藏在重重迷雾之后的真相。<br>特色游戏内容和玩法<br>-\t不同时间段的昼夜系统<br>-\t强大的剧情演出<br>-\t丰富多彩的支援人物<br>-\t不同流派的玩法选择",
